Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:44.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}家畜的安寧 虛偽的繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}葬送了死去餓狼的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:52.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}被囚的屈辱 是反擊之利箭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:57.47,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}於城牆的彼方 屠殺獵物的獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:03.02,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}迸裂的衝動 灼燒此身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:05.51,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}射穿黃昏之火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:09.71,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}紅蓮之弓矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==== ====ED JP==== ====
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:46.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}その夢は心の居場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:51.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}命より壊れやすきもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:57.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}何度でも捨てては見つけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:23:03.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}安らかに さあ眠れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}脈打つ衝動に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:14.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}願いは侵され
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:19.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}忘れてしまうほど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:25.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}また思い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:31.16,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}この美しき残酷な世界では
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.98,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}まだ生きていること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.83,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}なぜと問うばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:42.36,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}あー 僕達はこの強さ弱さで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:45.51,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}何を守るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:51.73,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(0,500)}もう理性などないならば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==== ====ED CN==== ====
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:46.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}那夢想是心的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:51.56,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}比生命更加脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:57.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}不斷拋棄不斷拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:23:03.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}安詳地 睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}脈搏跳動的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:14.54,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}侵犯著這願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:19.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}即將忘卻之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:25.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}又再次想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:31.16,ED-CN-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}在這美麗而又殘酷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.98,ED-CN-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}我不斷問詢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.83,ED-CN-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}為何苟延殘喘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:42.36,ED-CN-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}啊 無論我們是強是弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:45.51,ED-CN-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333}如果失去了理性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:51.73,ED-CN-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(0,500)}還能守護什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==== ====IN EN==== ====
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.70,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}She said She gave all her love to me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.86,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}We dreamt a new life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:59.76,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,500)}Some place to be at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.46,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,500)}But things changed... Suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:11.06,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,800)}I lost my dreams in this disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.64,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}I'm crying
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.70,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,500)}Missing my lover
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:23.08,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,500)}I don't have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:27.44,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,500)}On my side forever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:32.30,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}Oh, Where is my lover
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:37.22,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,500)}And I got no power
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:44.52,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,800)}I'm standing alone. No way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:51.22,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,800)}Calling out your name
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==== ====IN CN==== ====
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}她說她將她所有的愛都給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}我們夢想過新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:59.76,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}一個充滿和平的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}但世事難料... 轉瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:11.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,800)\c&HE5E5E5&}我在這場災難中失去了我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.64,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}我悲痛慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}失去了我的愛人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:23.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:27.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}再也沒有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:32.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,200)\c&HE5E5E5&}噢, 我的愛人在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:37.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,500)\c&HE5E5E5&}而我沒有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:44.52,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,800)\c&HE5E5E5&}我孤獨一人的站著 迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:51.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(200,800)\c&HE5E5E5&}呼喚著你的名字
